    <item>
      <title>MoneyGram 贷款重新定价在早期交易困难后完成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/moneygram-s-loan-repricing-completed-after-early-deal-struggles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于评级较低的公司纷纷降低借贷成本，而投资者对高息债务的渴求，速汇金国际公司 (MoneyGram International Inc.) 上周在提高报价条件后，完成了 3.98 亿美元杠杆贷款的重新定价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/moneygram-s-loan-repricing-completed-after-early-deal-struggles</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 19:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士贸易商 Sucafina 将收购越南顶级罗布斯塔咖啡生产商 Mercon 的资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/sucafina-to-buy-mercon-assets-in-top-robusta-producer-vietnam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士咖啡贸易商 Sucafina SA 将收购 Mercon Coffee Corp 在越南的子公司，扩大其在全球最大速溶咖啡用罗布斯塔咖啡豆生产商中的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/sucafina-to-buy-mercon-assets-in-top-robusta-producer-vietnam</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 19:33:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
